  m_functionName: 
  m_description: 'Simulates height map parallax by dynamically offsetting UV coordinates
    based on

    view direction and a height map texture.


    This function modifies
    the input UVs using a parallax factor and the sampled

    height map, creating
    the illusion of depth without altering geometry.

    A toggle input allows enabling
    or disabling the simulation at runtime.


    When disabled, the original UVs
    are passed through unchanged.'
